Painting competitionBringing out several means to conserve fuel and consider serious measures to make the planet greener, a number of students participated in the spot painting competition that was held at Gayatri Vidya Parishad MLBT School on Saturday. Highlighting the theme ‘Towards Cleaner Fuels…Greener Planet’, participants wielded the brush to fill the canvas with colours. The event was organised jointly by the Hindustan Petroleum Corporation Limited and the Petroleum Conservation and Research Association to mark Oil and Gas Conservation Fortnight – 2016’.